# ── Credentials (never commit) ───────────────────────────────────────────────
talosconfig
kubeconfig
*.key
*.crt
# NOTE: keys/signing_key.pem is intentionally NOT gitignored.
# It is a build-time reproducibility key embedded in the kernel via
# CONFIG_MODULE_SIG_KEY. It is not a secret in the traditional sense — exposing
# the private key only means someone could build modules that load in THIS kernel.
# Committing it ensures every build uses the same key and prevents "module key
# unavailable" boot failures. See scripts/00-setup-keys.sh and README Section 12.2.

# ── Build outputs (large binaries, reproduced by scripts) ────────────────────
dist/
imager-out-*/
*.efi
*.efi.zst
*.raw
*.raw.zst
*.raw.xz

# ── Intermediate build artifacts ─────────────────────────────────────────────
*.xz
*.zst
initramfs-*.xz
initramfs-*.zst
kernel-modules-*/
systemd-boot.efi

# ── macOS system files ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
__MACOSX/

# ── Editor / IDE ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# ── Claude Code internal state ────────────────────────────────────────────────
.claude/

# ── Intermediate imager output directories ────────────────────────────────────
imager-out-v*/
